  "tosSection1Title": "Acceptance of תנאים",
  "tosSection1Para1": "By creating an account, accessing, or using the {appName} mobile application (\"the Service\"), you agree to be bound by these תנאים of Service (\"Terתנאים If you do not agree to these Tתנאים you must not access or use the Service.",
